#, no-wrap
msgid "make"
msgstr "make"

#. type: <p><example>
#: maint-guide.en.sgml:1726
msgid ""
"<prgn>dh_auto_test</prgn> usually executes the following if <file>Makefile</"
"file> exists with the <tt>test</tt> target. <footnote><p>It actually looks "
"for the first available target of <tt>test</tt> or <tt>check</tt> in "
"<file>Makefile</file> and execute it.</p></footnote>"
msgstr ""
"<prgn>dh_auto_test</prgn> exécute normalement ce qui suit si <file>Makefile</"
"file> fournit la cible <tt>test</tt> : <footnote><p>En fait il recherche la "
"première cible disponible parmi <tt>test</tt> et <tt>check</tt> dans "
"<file>Makefile</file> et l'exécute.</p></footnote>"

#. type: <example></example>
#: maint-guide.en.sgml:1728
#, no-wrap
msgid "make test"
msgstr "make test"

